{"title":"土地的音乐","authors":["钟鸣"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":6,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕牛翻开田野的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"季节将心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播入土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一帧彩色的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风春雨成了画外音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与春光同行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁铧和耕牛一起劳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有流行曲红歌星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而一种来自田野的声乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给土地烙下深沉的光影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民用双脚　演奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个春夏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏在牛背上的歌声中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫地遍野　飞行"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}